Title: Fermions on the Light-Front
Author: M. Burkardt (NMSU)
Comments: 9 pages, to appear in the proceedings of the CSSM Workshop on
  Light-Cone QCD and Nonperturbative Hadron Physics, Adelaide, Australia, Dec.
  13-21, 1999
\\
  Issues that are specific for formulating fermions in light-cone quantization
are discussed. Special emphasis is put on the use of parity invariance in the
non-perturbative renormalization of light-cone Hamiltonians.
